      • getContainer

        PersistentContainer getContainer()
        Return the low level PersistentContainer held by this DatabaseEngine. Low level PersistentContainer can be some storage object used by this database for persistence operations. In other words this method will be returned an instance of Storage,StorageGraph,StorageManager,StoragePool.
        Returns:
        low level PersistentContainer
        Since:
        1.0
